o remainder. Thus, the division is straightforward and yields an integer result.\n\nThe whole number result is:\n\n\\(\\boxed{1}\\)<｜end▁of▁sentence｜>'], label: None, reward: {'reward': 1.0, 'accuracy': 1, 'format_score': 1}
